{"tid":1040264,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【豚王母企】賞之味今起招股　入場費約3535元","createTime":"2019-02-28T03:39:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T05:13:58.000Z","uid":38451,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7605dc483685e489570fa7d3afaeefd900515d1f","tid":1040264,"uid":38451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T03:39:26.000Z","msg":"豚王母企賞之味擬發售1.25億股，當中90%國際發售，10%本港公開發售，招股價介乎0.4元至0.7元，集資最多8750萬元，以每手5,000股計算，入場費約3535.27元，獨家保薦人為富比資本。<br />\n<br />\n公司今日起至3月4日（下周一）招股，並於3月15日掛牌。<br />\n<br />\n公司擬把約60.6%集資所得用於在香港開設新店；約20.0%將用作擴張香港的現有中央廚房；約5.2%將用作提升品牌知名度；約4.4%將用作提升營運能力及效率；約9.8%將用作一般營運資金。"},{"pid":"6587f2757c4d2537a38180c1f74b4dd6f40a781d","tid":1040264,"uid":33728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T03:40:33.000Z","msg":"買100手"},{"pid":"a41697d53273ea39e7941ba4034af37f6f42dd27","tid":1040264,"uid":76747,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T03:41:11.000Z","msg":"連登仔又有新玩具"},{"pid":"e3327a229b47d6cbef6fe8febbc1d25bc0de7f50","tid":1040264,"uid":470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T03:42:59.000Z","msg":"仲垃圾過毛記<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0251aed5176d2006a8563bde16bb2956e452ae6c","tid":1040264,"uid":34508,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T03:53:42.000Z","msg":"以前喺銅鑼灣幾好食 依家愈黎愈垃圾<br />\n仲上埋大陸開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710a700faad76384c2d0c96e4b1941ae4347d5c5","tid":1040264,"uid":28307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0251aed5176d2006a8563bde16bb2956e452ae6c","tid":1040264,"uid":34508,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T03:53:42.000Z","msg":"以前喺銅鑼灣幾好食 依家愈黎愈垃圾<br />\n仲上埋大陸開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T04:05:58.000Z","msg":"初期中期都還好 依家真係明顯難食咗好多"},{"pid":"fda407908c4701207465d813265f44b96df542ea","tid":1040264,"uid":7096